Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:06.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:09.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:16.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:21.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 结果还是没找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:26.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:29.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很重要的话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鹅肝酱饭团 鱼翅饭团 珠鸡肉饭团 松露饭团\N鱼子酱饭团 咸鱼干饭团 榴莲饭团 甜瓜饭团 番茄豆汤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:31.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 还有没有番茄口汤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:37.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:42.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们已经不卖番茄口汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,胡子绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫纱绘 佐仓纱绘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,之前给你看照片的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:58.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊 你还在便利店打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 你在找什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那那个叫苍乃的女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以全部都是我引起的 懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 那那个叫依人的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 别放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,破烂兔拳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你在意也无济于事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 饭还没买回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒很想吃吃看鹅肝酱口味饭团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你总是这样扯开话题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也有刚史的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不太信任我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我并不是不信任你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉学会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这种生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为如果不这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,会很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人吧 这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有骗人 拜托 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,番茄口汤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 番茄口汤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,胡子绅士来买的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:39.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:49.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天只上半天课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你一个人过一整天会不会太寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:57.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我打扰到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 不过 平底锅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候应该采取的措施是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:17.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:22.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 用小火慢慢炖是窍门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名没说过不可以来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:37.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样的话 苍乃就变成一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依特制法国吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有一半是苍乃做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 正好肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:04.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,味道如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:10.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:13.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:23.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然吃饭要像这样和苍乃 依人一起吃才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:24.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依一直都做料理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这个问题由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,石月 你来解答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,石月？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:45.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 石月她身体有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很温柔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:55.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说是为了朋友来找番茄口汤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他往哪里走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他说有目标 找一会再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我明早再来这里拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 祝你们姐弟度过一个舒适的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也快点去吃吧 我来洗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:40.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 突然这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我和姐姐的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:54.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回来是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么姐姐你也别隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有隐瞒 什么也没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:07.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到茉莉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 但我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:22.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我刺伤了茉莉 姐姐让我坚信那是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你认识茉莉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐对我隐瞒了什么 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有隐瞒你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想和依人两个人在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:58.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 我什么都不要 什么都不考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:08:59.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么依人要生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,突然冒出来的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么四方茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:14.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧 茉莉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的弟弟 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,用尽我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我有多肮脏 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道的是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:36.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃是夜祸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:25.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我平时积德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:35.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 男人都那么迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:43.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的胡子眼镜男人 看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:53.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了这种理由追我到这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因为无论如何都想见茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:57.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:10.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 这个人不是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你别牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请帮我传达一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫依人现在很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:23.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:29.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我走在街上 偶然遇见她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会帮你传达的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小依的姐姐 叫石月真名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依总是受您照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是真名？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,御池学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 今天正好是开学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,应该叫姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:36.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫森宫依人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:49.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫真名 石月真名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:09.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依实在隐瞒不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老实说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去苍乃家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:17.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:20.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没遵守约定 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 依人也回到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又像往常那样快乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没一起睡了 一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:08.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:14.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于想起来了 这里发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:21.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 虽然只是一些片段 但还是想起了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,穿和服的茉莉 还有那个洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和茉莉很早以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也许早在几百年以前就认识了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是夜祸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:50.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我却有以前的茉莉和姐姐还有自己身影的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:53.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人在过去确实存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:02.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 任何人都只能活一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那时候就已经死掉的依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:28.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐一下 这就是知道真相的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,必须的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:31.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:34.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:22.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:41.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人 依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是活祭 却还一直活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然后苍乃就执迷于
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,重新制造你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就终于
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 苍乃制造出来的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,植入了依人的记忆的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 还没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,睡眠不足可是皮肤的天敌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫依人的男孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:30.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定就那么崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚史
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他本人想知道真相的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:47.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了活在不安 痛苦 和真实中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也无法去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:00.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:39.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 依人是怎样一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和现在的我一样的性格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:45.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还有姐姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:46.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都是以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已经忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我记住的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是依人 连人类也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:16.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个扮演过去的依人的可怜幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但也并不是没有存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:20.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:33.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以亲吻 也可以握手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你确实在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:42.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然受着依人的记忆影响 你自己也在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,自己做着自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:51.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:56.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明应该在的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没办法了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:25.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:28.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:38.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这把刀的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:35.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依终于也学会手刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:37.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:41.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我小依小姐 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:42.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,(><) x1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:43.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,(><) x2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:44.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,(><) x3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:20.03,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(480,480)\bord3\shad0\blur6}摇晃的幻境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:45.44,FBT,NTP,560,0,224,,梦想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:57.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽根が白く光り 眩しく飛んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:04.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心だけ乗せて欲しいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:12.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たい手を伸ばす 届かない…知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:19.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどいま触れたい君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:26.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}懐かしい風には あの頃の舟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:34.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}幻が思い出を見せた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:44.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れない」誰かの声が切なく響く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:49.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}始まる予感にふるえて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:57.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れたい」願う自分がわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:09.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}待っている 揺られながら夢ひとつを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:57.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}雪白闪亮的羽毛飞向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:04.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它要是能带上我的心意多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:12.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出冰冷的双手 明明知道触摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:19.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可是现在想碰触到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:26.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人怀念的微风像那时候的小船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:34.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}呈现出梦幻的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:44.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「不要忘记」耳边想起悲伤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:49.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}害怕那要发生什么的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:57.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「想要忘记」却不知自己为何如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:09.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}带着一个梦想和心中的动摇 等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:17.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いろ褪せた頁の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:22.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}瞳閉じれば蘇る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:26.82,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あどけない少女の祈り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:31.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽ばたけよ 希望の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:36.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}嘆く間もなく 時は流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:40.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとり立ち止まるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:47.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夢守る調べ 口ずさむの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:52.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}人々が眠りにつけば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:58.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}また会う日の 願い紡げるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愛の糸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさを誘う おとぎ話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:10.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたから教わったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:20.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}戻りましょう そっとあの頃の想いに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:17.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}褪色书页的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:22.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每当闭上眼就会浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:26.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天真烂漫的少女的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:31.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}展翅吧 飞向希望的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:36.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不知不觉叹息中时间在流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:40.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而一个人停留着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:47.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻吟唱着守护梦境的小调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:52.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}人们安稳入眠的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:58.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就会编织 再次相会的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那爱的丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}勾起往日温馨回忆的 童话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:10.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是你告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:20.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}让我们回到那安宁的时刻吧
